    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克在领导层威胁下拒绝设定选举日期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/sunak-resists-call-to-set-election-date-amid-leadership-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)拒绝了盟友关于确定英国大选日期的建议，他们称这将有助于他阻止下个月保守党叛乱分子对领导权的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/sunak-resists-call-to-set-election-date-amid-leadership-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非反对派协议有可能在选举前瓦解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/south-african-opposition-pact-risks-unraveling-before-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由南非 11 个反对党组成的联盟旨在在下个月的选举中推翻非洲人国民大会，该联盟的两名最大成员表示，如果没有彻底的获胜者，他们可能与执政党共同执政，该联盟面临瓦解的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/south-african-opposition-pact-risks-unraveling-before-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰战争进入新阶段，能源聚焦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/war-in-ukraine-enters-new-phase-with-power-oil-gas-attacked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着俄罗斯和乌克兰的贸易对石油、天然气和电力设施造成打击，其附带损害正在全球市场上显现出来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/war-in-ukraine-enters-new-phase-with-power-oil-gas-attacked</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 04:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列对阵伊朗——他们之间的公开战争会是什么样子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/israel-versus-iran-what-an-open-war-between-them-could-look-like</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国及其欧洲盟友担心，4 月 1 日在叙利亚发生的导致数名伊朗军官死亡的袭击可能会将以色列和伊朗推向几十年来一直避免的边缘：公开战争。到目前为止，除了一个例外，伊朗一直利用代理人攻击以色列，而以色列则避免对伊朗领土进行空袭。现在，以色列正准备对大马士革的袭击进行报复，这一前景引发了人们对地区冲突的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/israel-versus-iran-what-an-open-war-between-them-could-look-like</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 02:36:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克将与莫迪会面，刺激特斯拉投资印度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/tesla-s-musk-to-meet-modi-spurring-india-invesment-speculation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司首席执行官埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)将访问印度并会见印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪(Narendra Modi)，这引发了人们对这家美国公司在印度全国大选开始前投资的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/tesla-s-musk-to-meet-modi-spurring-india-invesment-speculation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 05:55:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
